Text: thanks blackcanary! hey when you have time, would you please search for youngblood - bloodsport #2 from 2003? it never got a proper release but limited copies were sold at a wizard convention. i downloaded #1 and it's so terrible that i must read #2. unsure if it's ever been scanned though. if anyone can find it, it's you!
